<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 18:15:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>报道：谷歌将以 230 亿美元收购以色列初创公司</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/report-google-to-pay-23-billion-for-israeli-startup/00000190-b244-d7ee-af9c-ff4c670b0000</link><description>据《华尔街日报》报道，对 Wiz 的收购将成为谷歌历史上最大的一笔收购</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 17:45:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/report-google-to-pay-23-billion-for-israeli-startup/00000190-b244-d7ee-af9c-ff4c670b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 282 天：以色列军队确认杀害哈马斯汗尤尼斯旅指挥官</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-282-idf-confirms-killing-commander-of-hamas-khan-yunis-brigade/00000190-b235-d9c3-ad99-bf3770520000</link><description>以色列国防军：仍在评估针对哈马斯军事首领穆罕默德·德伊夫的暗杀企图；哈马斯汗尤尼斯旅指挥官被杀 ■ 以色列四名士兵在汽车撞击事件中受伤；袭击者被枪杀 ■ 内塔尼亚胡祝愿特朗普在暗杀企图后“早日康复” ■ 战争进入 282 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 17:18:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-282-idf-confirms-killing-commander-of-hamas-khan-yunis-brigade/00000190-b235-d9c3-ad99-bf3770520000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府计划将男性义务兵役期延长至三年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-government-set-to-extend-mandatory-military-service-for-men-to-three-years/00000190-b1df-d7ee-af9c-ffdfa5280000</link><description>以色列总检察长在一份意见中表示，在不征召犹太学院学生的情况下增加军人负担是违宪的。该法案将送交议会批准</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 17:07:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-government-set-to-extend-mandatory-military-service-for-men-to-three-years/00000190-b1df-d7ee-af9c-ffdfa5280000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普和德伊夫的共同点不仅仅是暗杀未遂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/trump-and-deif-share-a-lot-more-than-attempted-assassinations/00000190-b1fb-d3c7-ab94-bfff0af50000</link><description>唐纳德·特朗普和穆罕默德·德伊夫是两位暴力先知，他们属于极有影响力的稀有人物。 ■ 刺杀哈桑·纳斯鲁拉将如何影响真主党？</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 16:31:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/trump-and-deif-share-a-lot-more-than-attempted-assassinations/00000190-b1fb-d3c7-ab94-bfff0af50000</guid></item><item><title>代夫的“死亡”：以色列的暗杀企图如何实现加沙停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/deifs-death-how-israels-assassination-attempt-could-deliver-a-gaza-cease-fire/00000190-b199-d96f-a1f6-ff9948640000</link><description>周六针对加沙穆罕默德·德伊夫的空袭只是以色列对哈马斯军事首领的最新一次暗杀企图。无论他的命运如何，对这位被美化为“抵抗”传奇的大屠杀凶手的打击对以色列、哈马斯和加沙有着丰富的影响</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 16:00:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/deifs-death-how-israels-assassination-attempt-could-deliver-a-gaza-cease-fire/00000190-b199-d96f-a1f6-ff9948640000</guid></item><item><title>使一些欧洲犹太人对艾滋病毒产生抵抗力的突变也是一个坏消息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/how-a-mutation-making-some-european-jews-hiv-resistance-became-really-bad-news/00000190-b15a-d9f4-afd5-fbdff5890000</link><description>赋予一些德系犹太人艾滋病毒抵抗力的相同突变也使他们死于西尼罗河热的风险更高，西尼罗热病在以色列比在他们祖先的北欧国家更为流行</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 15:15:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/how-a-mutation-making-some-european-jews-hiv-resistance-became-really-bad-news/00000190-b15a-d9f4-afd5-fbdff5890000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的忠实支持者将特朗普的暗杀企图与煽动总理联系起来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-loyalists-link-trump-assassination-attempt-with-incitement-against-pm/00000190-b174-d96f-a1f6-ff7ce91c0000</link><description>以色列右翼议员在社交媒体上将失败的暗杀企图比作针对内塔尼亚胡的煽动，利库德集团的一位部长表示，今天针对内塔尼亚胡的煽动“比拉宾被谋杀之前存在的煽动更糟糕”</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 15:15:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-loyalists-link-trump-assassination-attempt-with-incitement-against-pm/00000190-b174-d96f-a1f6-ff7ce91c0000</guid></item><item><title>早在加沙战争之前，以色列人就一直以否认为策略</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/living-in-denial-as-an-israeli-strategy/00000190-b073-d9c3-ad99-bd734b750000</link><description>以色列公众对加沙战争的无知态度是自 1967 年开始的立场的延伸。开放社会如何鼓励系统性地否认虐待行为？</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 14:44:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/living-in-denial-as-an-israeli-strategy/00000190-b073-d9c3-ad99-bd734b750000</guid></item><item><title>以色列司法部长告诉法院，强迫他选择法院院长是“司法改革”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-to-top-court-compelling-me-to-pick-court-president-is-judicial-reform/00000190-b166-d9f4-afd5-fbef23470000</link><description>司法部长表示，要求最高法院强迫他召开司法遴选委员会的请愿书是“试图将公众排除在委员会之外”，接受请愿书将“损害公众对司法机构的信任”</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 14:41:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-to-top-court-compelling-me-to-pick-court-president-is-judicial-reform/00000190-b166-d9f4-afd5-fbef23470000</guid></item><item><title>亚美尼亚完全有权承认巴勒斯坦国。以色列无权谴责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-14/ty-article-opinion/.premium/armenia-has-every-right-to-recognize-palestinian-state-israel-is-wrong-to-reprimand-it/00000190-b0d4-d7ee-af9c-ffdcde6c0000</link><description>亚美尼亚不欠虚伪的以色列任何责任。犹太人和亚美尼亚人的共同命运本应使以色列和亚美尼亚成为盟友，但以色列国却选择了不同的道路。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 14:20:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-14/ty-article-opinion/.premium/armenia-has-every-right-to-recognize-palestinian-state-israel-is-wrong-to-reprimand-it/00000190-b0d4-d7ee-af9c-ffdcde6c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列中部地区发生冲撞袭击，四名以色列国防军士兵受伤，袭击者被击毙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/four-wounded-in-central-israel-ramming-attack-attacker-shot-dead-by-police/00000190-b134-d96f-a1f6-ff3ce71d0000</link><description>一名警察开枪射杀了单独行动的嫌疑人。以色列警察局长沙卜泰表示，由于哈马斯领导人穆罕默德·代夫遭到暗杀，警方加强了警戒，增加了警力。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 13:50:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/four-wounded-in-central-israel-ramming-attack-attacker-shot-dead-by-police/00000190-b134-d96f-a1f6-ff3ce71d0000</guid></item><item><title>他们能改变以色列吗？六名以色列妇女讲述她们示威的原因</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/can-they-change-israel-six-israeli-women-on-why-they-demonstrate/00000190-a117-dbad-adfc-f59f14580000</link><description>过去两年，示威活动占据了以色列公共领域。六位持六种不同观点的活动人士解释了以色列最让他们烦恼的是什么</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 11:54:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/can-they-change-israel-six-israeli-women-on-why-they-demonstrate/00000190-a117-dbad-adfc-f59f14580000</guid></item><item><title>以色列陆军战地观察员因在躲避导弹袭击时遗弃装备而接受审判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/idf-field-spotters-put-on-trial-for-abandoning-equipment-while-escaping-missile-attack/00000190-b07d-d739-a5b2-fd7fb5560000</link><description>士兵们表示，当他们位于以色列北部的前哨基地遭到来自黎巴嫩的反坦克导弹袭击时，指挥官指示他们留下这些装备。装备包括头盔、防弹衣和背包</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 10:12:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/idf-field-spotters-put-on-trial-for-abandoning-equipment-while-escaping-missile-attack/00000190-b07d-d739-a5b2-fd7fb5560000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院质疑极端正统派部长在教育部的角色合法性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/court-questions-legitimacy-of-ultra-orthodox-ministers-role-in-education-ministry/00000190-b025-d7ee-af9c-ff2d05ee0000</link><description>法庭听证会显示，在以色列教育部未能回应去年代表《国土报》提出的信息自由请求后，没有正式文件证明沙斯·海姆·比顿在以色列教育部的职责</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 09:02:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/court-questions-legitimacy-of-ultra-orthodox-ministers-role-in-education-ministry/00000190-b025-d7ee-af9c-ff2d05ee0000</guid></item><item><title>访问以色列一年后，在贝鲁特附近发现了著名的僧海豹尤利娅</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/nature-environment/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/famous-monk-seal-yulia-spotted-near-beirut-a-year-after-visit-to-israel/00000190-adc1-d04d-a3d6-addd83f70000</link><description>大约一年前，这只海豹在雅法海滩上出现，俘获了以色列人的心，最后一次出现是在加沙附近。米娅·埃拉萨尔博士说：“我们很高兴知道她不再身处战区。”她补充说，她正在等待尤利娅返回土耳其的家。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 05:23:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/nature-environment/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/famous-monk-seal-yulia-spotted-near-beirut-a-year-after-visit-to-israel/00000190-adc1-d04d-a3d6-addd83f70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军证实哈马斯指挥官汗·尤尼斯被杀；报告：加沙中部15人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article-live/idf-attacked-central-headquarters-in-syria-in-response-to-drones-launched-toward-eilat/00000190-af03-d7ee-af9c-ff0b3f5a0000</link><description>以色列中部拉姆拉附近发生汽车撞车袭击，四名士兵受伤，其中两人伤势严重 ■ 以色列内阁同意将以色列国防军义务兵役期从 32 个月延长至 36 个月，以应对人力短缺问题 ■ 哈马斯表示，汗去世后，军事首长穆罕默德·德伊夫“状况良好”周六尤尼斯遇袭 ■ 哈马斯消息来源称，谈判仍在进行中，此前有相互矛盾的报道称，袭击后谈判被终止 ■ 以色列北部响起警笛声</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 03:55:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article-live/idf-attacked-central-headquarters-in-syria-in-response-to-drones-launched-toward-eilat/00000190-af03-d7ee-af9c-ff0b3f5a0000</guid></item><item><title>杀死德伊夫不足以确保哈马斯失去对加沙的平民控制</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/killing-deif-wont-be-enough-to-ensure-hamas-loss-of-civilian-control-of-gaza/00000190-af11-d7ee-af9c-ff19c21b0000</link><description>穆罕默德·德伊夫可能被暗杀并不意味着以色列无需立即提出切实可行的工作计划。以色列必须找到替代巴勒斯坦文职政府的解决方案。内塔尼亚胡拒绝让巴勒斯坦权力机构在加沙发挥作用，疏远了那些能够完成从文职政府中消灭哈马斯任务的人</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 03:29:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/killing-deif-wont-be-enough-to-ensure-hamas-loss-of-civilian-control-of-gaza/00000190-af11-d7ee-af9c-ff19c21b0000</guid></item><item><title>穆罕默德·德伊夫，哈马斯领导人，在以色列至少七次暗杀企图中幸存</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/mohammed-deif-hamas-leader-who-survived-at-least-seven-israeli-assassination-attempts/00000190-ae33-dda3-adf9-ee775b8f0000</link><description>德伊夫连续 30 年高居以色列通缉名单之首，并导致数百名以色列人死亡。 1992 年，他领导的一个组织绑架并试图杀害一名士兵阿隆·卡拉瓦尼 (Alon Karavani)，这是他实施的第一次恐怖行动</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 01:25:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-14/ty-article/.premium/mohammed-deif-hamas-leader-who-survived-at-least-seven-israeli-assassination-attempts/00000190-ae33-dda3-adf9-ee775b8f0000</guid></item><item><title>世界法院下周就以色列占领西岸和东耶路撒冷发表意见</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-13/ty-article/.premium/world-court-to-issue-opinion-on-israeli-west-bank-occupation-east-jerusalem-next-week/00000190-ada9-df48-afba-bdfb8c0a0000</link><description>该咨询意见将于周五发布，将讨论以色列控制西岸和东耶路撒冷的合法性以及是否构成永久吞并，可能裁定以色列必须无条件放弃对这些地区的占有</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 20:32:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-13/ty-article/.premium/world-court-to-issue-opinion-on-israeli-west-bank-occupation-east-jerusalem-next-week/00000190-ada9-df48-afba-bdfb8c0a0000</guid></item><item><title>阿根廷将哈马斯列为恐怖组织以示对以色列的支持</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/americas/2024-07-13/ty-article/argentina-designates-hamas-a-terrorist-group-in-show-of-support-for-israel/00000190-ad07-d45b-a197-ef075e250000</link><description>总统哈维尔·米莱 (Javier Milei) 办公室援引了 10 月 7 日的袭击事件以及该组织与伊朗的密切关系，阿根廷将 20 世纪 90 年代的两起爆炸事件归咎于伊朗</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 19:22:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/americas/2024-07-13/ty-article/argentina-designates-hamas-a-terrorist-group-in-show-of-support-for-israel/00000190-ad07-d45b-a197-ef075e250000</guid></item></channel></rss>